{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b8adf70967","title":"对军队同志的教导","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4a898a098c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"b8adf70967"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/50-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji50":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2d982b4677","type":"title","text":"对军队同志的教导","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"b8adf70967"},{"id":"6e6d1bd5ad","type":"paragraph","text":"有了错误就检讨就改正，改了就好了，只要讲三句话就行了。一句话：错了：二句话：是什么错就是什么错，在这个问题上或那个问题上是方向错了就承认这个问题上方向错了；第三句话：就改正。这样就好了。公开检查比不公开好，高姿态检查比低姿态好，早检查比晚检查好。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"b8adf70967"},{"id":"5346e02a07","type":"paragraph","text":"军队这几年群众工作做得少，错了改了就好，也不给处分，也不要治罪。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"b8adf70967"}],"page":{"id":"b96f29b67d","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"b8adf70967","start":32,"end":32}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"053a71ccb0","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自周总理 1967 年 7 月 7 日接见山西代表时的讲话）","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b8adf70967"},{"id":"281e748f14","type":"paragraph","text":"有了错误就检讨就改正，改了就好了，只要讲三句话就行了。一句话：错了；二句话：是什么错就是什么错，在这个问题上或那个问题上是方向错了就承认这个问题上方向错了；第三句话：就改正。这样就好了。公开检查比不公开好，高姿态检查比低姿态好，早检查比晚检查好。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b8adf70967"},{"id":"31785df5d3","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自××在 1967 年 7 月 7 日在昆明讲话）","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b8adf70967"},{"id":"5833cfaa57","type":"paragraph","text":"军队这几年群众工作做得少，错了改了就好，也不给处分，也不要治罪。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b8adf70967"},{"id":"5980cb4d8d","type":"title","text":"对军队同志的教导","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b8adf70967"}],"page":{"id":"e6e55d178d","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b8adf70967","start":612,"end":612}}}},"__N_SSG":true}